#

Banana Oatmeal Pancakes

15 min
$3.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Egg

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-FreeDairy-Free (if using plant-based milk)

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastEasyHealthyQuick

Description

Fluffy pancakes made with wholesome oats and ripe bananas for a delicious and nutritious breakfast.

Ingredients

  • rolled oats: 1 cup
  • ripe banana: 1
  • egg: 1
  • milk (or plant-based milk): 1/2 cup
  • baking powder: 1 tsp
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • cinnamon: 1/2 tsp
  • salt: a pinch
  • butter or oil: for cooking
